Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta Ochiai here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the old man found out about me and Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do l do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, please stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Mahoko, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko, come home with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't go! l'm staying here with Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanada...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing awfully dirty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set that boy on Mahoko, just to get at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be joking! That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada and the others have nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm in love with Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little squeeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you don't come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll kick Sanada and his friends off this beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, give it a rest. Sanada...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arisugawa, l don't want to fight with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this beach is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say, l'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. l'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll leave Kenta and his friends alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go home, Mahoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, Sanada was the All-Japan Surfing Champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not about money for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves this beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All-Japan Surfing Champ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All-Japan Champ, you say? Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because he has a trophy doesn't make it true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We happen to have a champion surfer at our place too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won the Hawaiian Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, how about a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you win a surfing contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll let you keep your hotel on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we win, you have to leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a deal! No, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see you on this beach tomorrow at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't chicken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, after we win this contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the hotel will be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that girl to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, now l'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll never surf again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you want to win, you'll have to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mr. Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep that surfboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still love surfing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Mr. Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years ago, l killed my lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had just won the championship that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a typhoon coming, but l took her out onto the water anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lt'll be fine. Don't worry about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l was overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was swallowed by a monstrous wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada, it's not your...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l shouldn't have taken her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't have the right to go out on the water anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see. l didn't know goofy old Sanada had such a dark past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what, Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you tell Arisugawa the story, maybe he'll reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that old man would listen to any story!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there isn't anyone else who can surf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you know it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l practiced all night, so l'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll win that contest and get Mahoko back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Kenta and Mahoko have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't l make up my mind and do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if Kenta doesn't change his ways, there's nothing l can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want Kenta to be with another girl. l can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt must be wonderful to be loved so much by Mr. Sanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to be loved by Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to become a woman that Kenta will love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, do you think l'm a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l envy Kenta. At least l do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe he's afraid of these waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Wait up, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess there's no helping it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, get ready to help Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, aren't you worried about Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta would never cheat to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me, l'm worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This contest is too much for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having a little trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to admit defeat any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that Mr. Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be out there, he can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta's getting by on dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's about to get dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you ride the waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Grandpa's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could beat you in my sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way l'll lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, boy! ls that all you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Mr. Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! l don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys better do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? We're not doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l have to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arisugawa, you're a hell of a surfer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine. Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Mina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't know you were such a great surfer, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't felt this good in years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko, how about l teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it runs in the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada! You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to be my coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting weird this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm bored with this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying. What's with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't have anything to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing l have to tell you is to take care of Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l like you, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that... makes it hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l have one night with you before l go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now l remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l love Kenta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having his arms around me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l want it in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, l can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Come inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:05.39,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Kenta! Take care of Suwatee! -Shuree
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Kenta. Take care of Suwatee! Shuree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wind chime sounds awfully sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt reminds me that summer's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a bummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get moving! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cutie, want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how am l doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be beating me any time soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Arisugawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming around you, Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanada, keep your hands off my employee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the president's a surfjunkie again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really gotten tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder how Shuree's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Taking a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's from Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's Shuree! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm in Okinawa now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hitched a ride with a truck driver who brought me all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm working at a beach bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l think l've been pretty good for business!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, when l watch the sun sink into the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, Kenta, Mr. Sanada: it was short but sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now l'm getting mushy! So goodbye until l see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sounds happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess summer's almost over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't even remember my life without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.22,0:24:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.12,0:24:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.12,0:25:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... but... l'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.60,0:25:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, l love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.08,0:25:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.72,0:25:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.25,0:25:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too small, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.98,0:26:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.09,0:26:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.42,0:26:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.39,0:26:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.97,0:27:27.10,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sagashi tsuzuketeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.97,0:27:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have the one bright smile...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:34.61,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kagayaku sono egao{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that l've always been looking for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.22,0:27:40.28,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yume ni made miteta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.22,0:27:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These arms of yours that hold me tight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.86,0:27:47.49,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}dakishimeru sono tewo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.86,0:27:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...l have only dreamed about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.53,0:27:53.73,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Subetewa hajimatte ita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.53,0:27:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l remember when it started...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.93,0:28:02.54,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}deatta shunkan ni kizuita yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.93,0:28:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the day l saw you standing there.{\i0}
